<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 12:12:28 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>世界各地的穆斯林庆祝古尔邦节，朝觐者“用石头砸死魔鬼”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/hajj-pilgrims-stone-the-devil-as-muslims-celebrate-eid-al-adha-across-the-world/articleshow/111037950.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111037950.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 11:07:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/hajj-pilgrims-stone-the-devil-as-muslims-celebrate-eid-al-adha-across-the-world/articleshow/111037950.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国：德克萨斯州六月节事件发生大规模枪击事件，造成 2 人死亡、多人受伤</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-multiple-people-injured-in-texas-mass-shooting-at-juneteenth-event/articleshow/111036102.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111036102.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 09:10:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-multiple-people-injured-in-texas-mass-shooting-at-juneteenth-event/articleshow/111036102.cms</guid></item><item><title>“这将是国际货币基金组织的最后一次救助”：巴基斯坦总理谢里夫誓言让国家经济重回正轨</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/this-will-be-last-imf-bailout-pakistan-pm-sharif-vows-to-bring-nations-economy-back-on-track/articleshow/111036954.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111036954.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 10:18:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/this-will-be-last-imf-bailout-pakistan-pm-sharif-vows-to-bring-nations-economy-back-on-track/articleshow/111036954.cms</guid></item><item><title>据称俾路支青年第二次被巴基斯坦军队“强行失踪”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/baloch-youth-allegedly-forcefully-disappeared-for-second-time-by-pakistani-forces/articleshow/111036860.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111036860.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;一名名叫 Brahmdagh 的 18 岁俾路支青年在俾路支省 Kech 区 Daazin 地区第二次被强迫失踪，据称是被巴基斯坦军队强迫失踪。家人对他屡次失踪表示担忧。</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 09:52:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/baloch-youth-allegedly-forcefully-disappeared-for-second-time-by-pakistani-forces/articleshow/111036860.cms</guid></item><item><title>阿富汗塔利班政府表示将参加联合国主办的第三轮多哈会谈</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/afghan-taliban-govt-says-to-attend-third-round-of-un-hosted-doha-talks/articleshow/111036381.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111036381.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;塔利班当局将参加联合国在卡塔尔首都主办的第三轮阿富汗问题会谈。一名政府发言人周日向法新社通报了这一决定，这标志着与他们避免的上一轮谈判的转变。穆贾希德周日对当地媒体表示，派遣代表团被认为对阿富汗有利。代表团具体成员名单将适时公布。</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 09:16:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/afghan-taliban-govt-says-to-attend-third-round-of-un-hosted-doha-talks/articleshow/111036381.cms</guid></item><item><title>国际特赦组织敦促塔利班为女童重新开放中学</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/amnesty-international-urges-taliban-to-reopen-secondary-schools-for-girls/articleshow/111036333.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111036333.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;国际特赦组织呼吁塔利班为阿富汗女童重新开放中学。据阿富汗卡马出版社报道，该组织强调塔利班的“歧视性和不公正政策”剥夺了阿富汗女孩的受教育权。国际特赦组织强调，塔利班的行为违反了国际法。</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 09:11:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/amnesty-international-urges-taliban-to-reopen-secondary-schools-for-girls/articleshow/111036333.cms</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰峰会力求达成广泛共识 依靠俄罗斯结束战争</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/ukraine-summit-strives-for-broad-consensus-to-lean-on-russia-to-end-war/articleshow/111035645.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111035645.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 08:24:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/ukraine-summit-strives-for-broad-consensus-to-lean-on-russia-to-end-war/articleshow/111035645.cms</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰和平峰会聚焦核恐惧</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/nuclear-fears-in-focus-at-ukraine-peace-summit/articleshow/111035894.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111035894.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;周日举行的乌克兰国际和平峰会将注意力转向粮食安全、防止核灾难以及遣返被驱逐到俄罗斯的儿童等问题。目标是为结束正在进行的战争奠定基础。俄罗斯入侵两年多后，来自 90 多个国家的领导人和高级官员齐聚瑞士风景如画的度假胜地。</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 08:38:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/nuclear-fears-in-focus-at-ukraine-peace-summit/articleshow/111035894.cms</guid></item><item><title>英国在网络犯罪上升之际为选举安全进行“小白鼠”民意调查</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/uk-polls-guinea-pig-for-election-security-amid-rise-in-cyber-crimes/articleshow/111033365.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111033365.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt; 7 月 4 日的英国大选面临来自中国和俄罗斯等国家行为体的网络安全威胁，担心错误信息、数据泄露和个人攻击，带来内部混乱和公众操纵的风险。</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 08:37:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/uk-polls-guinea-pig-for-election-security-amid-rise-in-cyber-crimes/articleshow/111033365.cms</guid></item><item><title>熊猫外交：中国承诺新的“可爱”大熊猫将取代澳大利亚受欢迎的一对</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/panda-diplomacy-china-promises-new-adorable-pandas-to-replace-australias-popular-pair/articleshow/111033961.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111033961.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 06:43:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/panda-diplomacy-china-promises-new-adorable-pandas-to-replace-australias-popular-pair/articleshow/111033961.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列的“经济战争”扼杀了被占领的约旦河西岸</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israels-economic-war-chokes-occupied-west-bank/articleshow/111033742.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111033742.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;由于巴勒斯坦领土上的银行业面临挑战以及以色列银行对重要银行业务的潜在威胁，拉马拉的巴勒斯坦马戏团学校在购买设备方面面临财务障碍。这影响了 Imad Rabah 的塑料公司、Nakhleh Jubran 的酒类业务和 Musa Shamieh 的女装公司等企业。</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 06:14:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israels-economic-war-chokes-occupied-west-bank/articleshow/111033742.cms</guid></item><item><title>观看：超过 700 人在伦敦特拉法加广场练习瑜伽</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/watch-over-700-people-perform-yoga-at-londons-trafalgar-square/articleshow/111032682.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111032682.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 06:20:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/watch-over-700-people-perform-yoga-at-londons-trafalgar-square/articleshow/111032682.cms</guid></item><item><title>中国南方洪水袭来，其他地方气温酷热</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/flooding-hits-chinas-south-temperatures-sizzle-elsewhere/articleshow/111033468.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111033468.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 06:06:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/flooding-hits-chinas-south-temperatures-sizzle-elsewhere/articleshow/111033468.cms</guid></item><item><title>瑞典与伊朗达成突破性协议交换囚犯</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/sweden-and-iran-exchange-prisoners-in-breakthrough-deal/articleshow/111033217.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111033217.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 05:36:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/sweden-and-iran-exchange-prisoners-in-breakthrough-deal/articleshow/111033217.cms</guid></item><item><title>拜登抨击最高法院与奥巴马、克鲁尼、朱莉娅·罗伯茨筹款2800万美元</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/biden-slams-supreme-court-at-28-million-fundraiser-with-obama-clooney-julia-roberts/articleshow/111032799.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111032799.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;总统乔·拜登在洛杉矶与巴拉克·奥巴马和好莱坞名人举行的筹款活动上批评了美国最高法院，筹款活动筹集了 2800 万美元。</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 05:01:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/biden-slams-supreme-court-at-28-million-fundraiser-with-obama-clooney-julia-roberts/articleshow/111032799.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列出于人道主义目的“战术暂停”加沙行动</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-to-give-its-gaza-action-tactical-pause-for-humanitarian-purposes/articleshow/111032555.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111032555.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;出于人道主义原因，以色列军队宣布“战术暂停”军事行动。此暂停时间为格林尼治标准时间 5:00 至 16:00，即印度标准时间 (IST) 上午 10:30 至上午 9:30。从 Kerem Shalom 路口到 Salah al-Din 路的道路向北延伸，将会出现暂停现象。</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 05:05:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-to-give-its-gaza-action-tactical-pause-for-humanitarian-purposes/articleshow/111032555.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦12岁女孩被迫嫁给72岁男子，警察救了她</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/12-year-old-girl-in-pakistan-forced-to-marry-72-year-old-man-cops-rescue-her/articleshow/111032123.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111032123.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;在巴基斯坦的查萨达镇，警方成功介入，阻止一名12岁女孩与一名名叫哈比卜汗的72岁男子结婚。当局逮捕了新郎和“Nikah Khwan”（主持婚礼的人），但女孩的父亲设法逃脱。根据《童婚法》，女孩的父亲、年长的新郎和“Nikah Khwan”已被立案。</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 04:56:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/12-year-old-girl-in-pakistan-forced-to-marry-72-year-old-man-cops-rescue-her/articleshow/111032123.cms</guid></item><item><title>“8岁儿童头部被击中”：目击者讲述美国水上乐园枪击事件的恐怖</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/8-year-old-struck-in-head-witnesses-recount-horror-of-us-waterpark-shooting/articleshow/111032066.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111032066.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;一名男子在美国底特律的防溅池开枪，造成至少 8 人受伤。奥克兰县治安官迈克·布沙尔 (Mike Bouchard) 表示，9 名受伤者中，有两人是儿童，其中一名 8 岁儿童头部中弹。枪手开了近 28 枪，并多次停下来重新装弹。最初的代表立即向受害者提供医疗援助。</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 04:24:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/8-year-old-struck-in-head-witnesses-recount-horror-of-us-waterpark-shooting/articleshow/111032066.cms</guid></item><item><title>台湾总统称中国将“消灭台湾”视为国家事业</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/china-views-taiwans-elimination-as-national-cause-taiwan-president-says/articleshow/111032207.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111032207.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;台湾总统赖清德周日表示，中国认为吞并和“消灭”台湾是一项重要的国家目标。他向军方最高学院的学员发表讲话，强调了解对手和抵制失败主义的重要性。上个月上任的黎智英不断面临来自中国的人身攻击，中国声称台湾是其领土。赖智就职后不久，北京在台湾周围进行了军事演习。</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 04:25:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/china-views-taiwans-elimination-as-national-cause-taiwan-president-says/articleshow/111032207.cms</guid></item><item><title>法官表示，密苏里州堕胎禁令并不是立法者强加宗教信仰</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/missouri-abortion-ban-wasnt-about-lawmakers-imposing-religious-beliefs-judge-says/articleshow/111031767.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111031767.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;密苏里州一名法官裁定，该州立法者的目的并不是通过严格的堕胎禁令来强加宗教信仰。这项禁令是在罗伊诉韦德案被推翻后颁布的，禁止密苏里州的大多数堕胎。</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 03:43:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/missouri-abortion-ban-wasnt-about-lawmakers-imposing-religious-beliefs-judge-says/articleshow/111031767.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>